App crashes, steals data, spreads misinformation, and completely disregards Apple App Store guidelines. MUST BE TAKEN DOWN! If you wanted to love this app, but couldn’t because it was actually supporting trump, go to TikTok and give it five stars. 

Personal Review:
As a proud American, I wanted to help out MY president: REASONABLE LOGIC. Trump represents clear and reasonable logic (as everyone knows), but I thought I’d list some alternative options that I personally would prefer and love to mix and match these “candidates” for the positions of president and Vice President:
-Michelle Obama
-Oprah Winfrey
-Charli D’Amelio (GADA- Get America Dancin’ Again)
-Estaban Julio Ricardo Montoya de la Rosa Ramírez (iykyk)
-Taylor Swift
-Harry Styles
-a cardboard cut out of Donald Trump with little wheels

A better app would be TikTok, although I’m sure he has people monitoring that now... or at least he would if he was smart.
